  <scopecontent id="aspace_c8c2a2bedc9bc60d4b39fc5af7229c59">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>Includes pamphlets concerning economics; articles by Morey concerning nutrition and the energy value of diets; and correspondence with J. Lossing Buck, L. A. Maynard, Lydia J. Roberts, Sybil L. Smith, Henry C. Sherman, Hildegard Kneeland, Mary S. Rose, Francis G. Benedict, Helen W. Atwater, Ruth Moore, Thorne M. Carpenter, E. P. Cathcart, F. C. Kelly, Faith M. Williams, Jonnie McCrery, John Leont'Ev, Milicent L. Hathaway, and Helen Canon.</p><p> Cornell University M.S. 1926, Ph.D. 1931.</p>  </scopecontent>
  <prefercite id="aspace_18930a619f86e35bdcdff4469ee8615a">
    <head>Cite As:</head>
<p>Nancy Booker Morey papers, #23-14-1465. Division of Rare and Manuscript Collections, Cornell University Library.</p><p> Guide to Initials Used in Correspondence</p><p> J. Lossing Buck (JLR) -- University of Nanking, but probably written from New York Office, 150 Fifth Avenue</p><p> Lydia J. Roberts (LJR) -- Prof. of Home Economics, University of Chicago. Chairman, Dept. of Home Economics</p><p> Sybil L. Smith (SLS) -- U.S.D.A., Office of Experiment Stations, Washington. Assistant in Experiment Station Administration</p><p> Hildegarde Kneeland (HK) -- Bureau of Home Economics, Washington</p><p> Mary S. Rose (MSR) -- Prof. of Nutrition, Teachers College, Columbia University</p><p> Henry C. Sherman (HCS) -- Department of Chemistry, Columbia University</p><p> Francis G. Benedict (FGB) -- Director of Nutrition Laboratory, Carnegie Institute of Washington, Boston</p><p> Helen W. Atwater (HWA) -- Editor, Journal of Home Economics, Washington</p><p> Ruth More (RM) -- U.S.D.A., Bureau of Home Economics, Washington</p><p> Thorne M. Carpenter (TMC) -- Carnegie Institute of Washington, Boston Nutrition Laboratory</p><p> E. P. Cathcart (EPC) -- University of Glasgow, Scotland</p><p> F. C. Kelly, Ph.D. (FCK) -- Imperial Bureau of Animal Nutrition, Aberdeen, Scotland</p><p> Faith M. Williams (FMW) -- Chief, Cost of Living Division, U.S Dept. of Labor, Washington</p><p> Jonnie McCrery (JM) -- Professor, Foods and Nutrition, Texas Technological College, Lubbock, Texas</p><p> Milicent L. Hathaway (MLH) -- Prof. of Physiology and Nutrition</p><p> Nancy Booker Morey (Mrs. Donald R.) (NBM)</p><p> Helen Canon (HC) -- Prof., Economics of Household &amp; Household Management, Cornell University</p>  </prefercite>
  <bioghist audience="internal" id="aspace_400dc2f7c14ceba34afcdf362f333c42">
    <head>Biographical / Historical</head>
<p>. Cornell University M.S. 1926, Ph.D. 1931.</p>  </bioghist>
